 Black Sabbath 的 Geezer Butler 表示他是 Slipknot 和 90 年代新金属爆炸的粉丝https://www.nme.com/news/music/black-sabbaths-geezer-butler-says-he-was-a-fan-of-slipknot-and-the-90s-nu-metal-explosion-3775639？ utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=black-sabbaths-geezer-butler-says-he-was-a-fan-of-slipknot-and-the-90s-nu-metal-explosionSurej Singh Wed, 17 Jul 2024 06:35:15 +0000 Music NewsNewsMetalNu-metalRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3775639 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/geezer-butler-slipknot@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="黑色安息日的 Geezer Butler 和 Slipknot 的 Corey Taylor 的合成图像。" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/geezer-butler-slipknot@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/geezer-butler-slipknot@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/geezer-butler-slipknot@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/geezer-butler-slipknot@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/geezer-butler-slipknot@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/geezer-butler-slipknot@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “看到当时出现的新乐队真是太棒了。每个乐队都有不同版本的金属”</p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/black-sabbaths-geezer-butler-says-he-was-a-fan-of-slipknot-and-the-90s-nu-metal-explosion-3775639">Black Sabbath 的 Geezer Butler 表示他是 Slipknot 的粉丝，而 90 年代的新金属爆炸</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/geezer-butler-slipknot@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="黑色安息日的 Geezer Butler 和 Slipknot 的 Corey Taylor 的合成图像。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/geezer-butler-slipknot@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/geezer-butler-slipknot@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/geezer-butler-slipknot@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/geezer-butler-slipknot@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/geezer-butler-slipknot@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/geezer-butler-slipknot@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-sabbath">Black Sabbath</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/geezer-butler">Geezer Butler</a>谈到了他对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slipknot">Slipknot</a>和 20 世纪 90 年代<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/nu-metal">新金属</a>爆炸的欣赏 - 看看这位传奇贝斯手在下面怎么说。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-clown-interview-tour-2024-tickets-new-material-3559353">活结乐队的小丑谈论 2024 年巡演和新材料：“这支乐队从未如此快乐”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位 Black Sabbath 联合创始人在接受<a href="https://knotfest.com/blogs/exclusive-interviews/black-hole-son-geezer-butler-on-sabbath-depression-the-devilish-side-of-religion-and-going-ultra-heavy" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Knotfest</em></a>采访时表示，他发现 90 年代的新金属浪潮很有趣，而且令人耳目一新。新金属的爆发催生了像 Slipknot、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/limp-bizkit">Limp Bizkit</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/korn">Korn</a>等乐队。</p><p> “当时我真的很喜欢金属，它也影响了我写的东西。看到当时出现的新乐队真是太棒了。如果你想称其为金属的话，每一种都有不同版本的金属。不同的版本，而不是只是对着麦克风尖叫，一切听起来都一样。真的很好，不同的乐队都出来了。显然，活结就是其中之一。太好了。” </p><figure id="attachment_3469750" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3469750" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3469750" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/geezer-butler@2000x1270.jpg" alt="老头管家" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/geezer-butler@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/geezer-butler@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/geezer-butler@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/geezer-butler@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/geezer-butler@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/geezer-butler@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3469750" class="wp-caption-text">老头巴特勒。图片来源：Kevin Mazur/WireImage</figcaption></figure><p>在聊天的其他地方，巴特勒提到<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fear-factory">Fear Factory</a>是他感兴趣的另一支乐队，并指出他们影响了他当时写的一些材料：“我当时真的很喜欢 Fear Factory，而且我一直在写所有的东西。”这些东西对安息日或奥兹来说太重了。我的侄子佩德罗（Howse，吉他手）有一支名为“疯狂天使”的乐队，他们就像一支超级鞭打乐队。所以当我和他一起写作时，它变得非常沉重，而且我不受我要写的歌词的限制。其中很多都是关于科幻小说的——有点像现在人工智能之类的东西正在发生的事情。”</p><p>本周早些时候，巴特勒透露，与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ozzy-osbourne">奥兹·奥斯本</a>类似， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/black-sabbaths-geezer-butler-says-the-beatles-were-a-massive-influence-on-the-band-3774914">披头士乐队对他来说是一个关键乐队</a>。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/2019_blacksabbath_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg">巴特勒和托尼·伊奥米此前都承认他们不听现代重金属</a>，巴特勒再次提到他对披头士乐队的偏爱，伊奥米说：“我确实倾向于听更古老的东西。更多的是经典的东西而不是新的东西，因为我对此更感兴趣。” </p><figure id="attachment_3774917" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3774917" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3774917" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/geezer-butler-performs-2019.jpg" alt="老头管家" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/geezer-butler-performs-2019.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/geezer-butler-performs-2019-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/geezer-butler-performs-2019-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/geezer-butler-performs-2019-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/geezer-butler-performs-2019-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/geezer-butler-performs-2019-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3774917" class="wp-caption-text"> Geezer Butler 在 2019 年 Louder Than Life 音乐节上表演。图片来源：Stephen J. Cohen/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>上个月，在活结乐队出人意料地宣布<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-announce-first-song-with-new-drummer-eloy-casagrande-long-may-you-die-3756860">与新鼓手埃洛伊·卡萨格兰德 (Eloy Casagrande) 合作创作第一首歌曲</a>《Long May You Die》之后六周，克拉汉 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-are-releasing-new-music-soon-says-clown-3768961">开玩笑说这支标志性金属乐队将“很快”发布新音乐</a>。</p><p>这位音乐家在接受<a href="https://www.revolvermag.com/music/slipknot-25-cover-story" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《Revolver》</em></a>采访时说道：“好吧，我可以说的一件事是：总会有新的活结音乐出现。但我们也说过，有一个过滤器，我们就是过滤器，这个过滤器必须经过每个人。</p><p> “当我告诉你我们的沟通做得更好时，现在将其应用于音乐方面的沟通。我可以说，音乐将会比你想象的更早出现，并以你无法想象的方式传递给你。”</p><p>在其他地方，Crahan 还在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-clown-interview-tour-2024-tickets-new-material-3559353">去年年底接受了<em>NME</em>采访，并公开了失落的 Slipknot 专辑《Look Outside Your Window》</a>以及该专辑何时可能发行。 </p><figure id="attachment_3600001" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3600001" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3600001" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/slipknot-corey-taylor@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/slipknot-corey-taylor@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/slipknot-corey-taylor@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/slipknot-corey-taylor@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/slipknot-corey-taylor@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/slipknot-corey-taylor@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/slipknot-corey-taylor@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3600001" class="wp-caption-text">活结乐团的科里·泰勒。图片来源：Venla Shalin/Redferns</figcaption></figure><p>尽管这张专辑原本应该在 Slipknot 的 We Are Not Your Kind 巡演期间发行，但由于新冠疫情，它被推迟到 2021 年。从那时起，主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/corey-taylor">科里·泰勒</a>就<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/corey-taylor-teases-release-of-slipknots-lost-album-look-outside-your-window-3482056">开玩笑说这张唱片将于今年某个时候到期</a>。</p><p> “艺术已经完成了。已经混在一起了已经掌握了。它肯定会在 2024 年发行，而且是一张很棒的专辑。科里是我最喜欢的歌手，你永远不会听到他以这张专辑中的方式唱歌，所以值得保留。这是一个如此不同、永恒的项目，”克拉汉说。</p><p>这支蒙面乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-announce-here-comes-the-pain-25th-anniversary-us-tour-with-knocked-loose-buy-tickets-3752450">将于今年夏天在北美开始他们的“Here Comes The Pain”25 周年巡演</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Knocked-Loose">Knocked Loose</a>等人将作为特邀嘉宾出现在演出中。 <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.com/slipknot-tickets/artist/763913?irgwc=1&amp;clickid=QHQVEUQchxyPR5sWCQS0k2gbUkHVWERWcSNiXA0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;impradid=2862475&amp;REFERRAL_ID=tmfeedbuyat2862475&amp;wt.mc_id=aff_BUYAT_2862475&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;impradname=NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;ircid=4272" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里查找剩余的门票</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-announce-2024-uk-and-europe-25th-anniversary-tour-buy-tickets-3556964">12 月份将在欧洲和英国举行一系列演出</a>，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-add-second-london-o2-show-to-25th-anniversary-uk-tour-2024-dates-buy-tickets-3559541">在伦敦 O2 剧院的两场演出</a>。您可以在下方查看 Slipknot 2024 年英国演出日期，并<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/slipknot-tickets/artist/763913?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium