x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/the-linda-lindas@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/the-linda-lindas@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/the-linda-lindas@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/the-linda-lindas@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-linda-lindas">琳达·琳达 (Linda Lindas)</a>宣布推出他们的第二张专辑《No Obligation》，并分享了一首新单曲《All In My Head》——请在下面查看。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/interview-the-linda-lindas-growing-up-songwriting-3278807">我们从与 Linda Lindas 的对话视频聊天中学到的五件事</a></strong></li></ul><p>昨天（7 月 16 日），这支洛杉矶摇滚乐队在社交媒体上宣布《No Obligation》，该专辑将于 10 月 11 日通过 Epitaph Records 发行。它现在可以以<a href="https://thelindalindas.ffm.to/vinyl" target="_blank" rel="noopener">黑胶唱片和其他物理格式进行预订</a>，并且还<a href="https://thelindalindas.ffm.to/noobligation">可以在数字流媒体平台上进行预保存</a>。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">我们的新专辑 No Obligation 将于 10 月 11 日发行<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f626.png" alt="😦" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/203c.png" alt="‼" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />今天你可以即兴演奏我们的新歌“All In My Head” <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f9e0.png" alt="🧠" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f4da.png" alt="📚" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/260e.png" alt="☎" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f308.png" alt="🌈" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" 